stration-and-governance/office-of-the-chief-financial-officer/financial-services/financial-information">Statements</a></li><li><a href="http://www.concordia.ca/about/administration-and-governance/office-of-the-chief-financial-officer/financial-services/contact-us/" class="affordance">Contact us</a></li></ul>		&nbsp;
