			</div>
			<h3>Who should I contact in Restricted Funds?</h3>
			<div class="content-hide" style="display:none;">
				<p>Please refer to the <a href="http://www.concordia.ca/about/administration-and-governance/office-of-the-chief-financial-officer/financial-services/departments/restricted-funds/contacts-by-area">Contacts by area</a> section under <strong>Departments</strong> - <strong>Restricted Funds</strong> on the left menu.</p>
